# Esparex Governance Pointer (Cursor)

Canonical AI governance, platform standards, and single execution paths live strictly in the repository SSOT files. This local file is a compatibility surface only and MUST NOT define independent rules.

Refer strictly to:
1. `docs/MASTER_DOCUMENT_REGISTRY.md` (Authoritative Registry)
2. `docs/ssot/DOMAIN_MODEL_SSOT.md` (Identity & Lifecycle SSOT)
3. `docs/ssot/API_CONTRACT_SSOT.md` (REST API Contract SSOT)
4. `docs/ssot/ARCHITECTURE_FLOW_SSOT.md` (Core Architecture Flows)
5. `docs/ssot/CI_CD_SSOT.md` (Pipelines & Quality Gates)
6. `docs/governance/GOVERNANCE_POLICY.md` (Developer Coding Standards)
7. `docs/governance/AI_GOVERNANCE_BOUNDARY.md` (AI Prompt Bounding rules)

**Mandatory Rule**: All documentation updates MUST be performed in-place on the canonical files registered in `docs/MASTER_DOCUMENT_REGISTRY.md`. Never create duplicate `_final`, `_latest`, or `_v2` files.
